              <div id="track-changes" class="section level2 boxtext" number="4.5">
              <div name="45_Track_changes" data-unique="45_Track_changes"></div><h2><span class="header-section-number">4.5</span> Track
            changes</h2>
              <div style="padding-left: 20px">
              <p>This group of panels shows up when using the functionalities provided
